author: Kelly McCarthy
title: New York coronavirus outbreak originated in Europe, new study finds
description: A new study from Mount Sinai found that the New York cases of COVID-19 originated from Europe.
content:
A new study has found evidence that the first COVID-19 cases in New York City originated in Europe and occurred as early as February.
